《'''尼基塔'''》（{{lang-en|''Nikita''}}）是一輯由[[CW電視台|CW電視台]]製作的[[美國|美國]][[電視連續劇|電視連續劇]]。此劇是基於1990年的[[法國|法國]]電影《[[尼基塔|尼基塔]]》（'''Nikita'''），以及1997年的同名電視劇《{{link-en|尼基塔女郎 (1997年電視劇)|La Femme Nikita|尼基塔女郎}}》（有時只簡稱'''Nikita'''）。此劇於2010年9月9日的[[東岸時間|東岸時間]]晚上9時在CW電視台首播<ref name="thursdays">{{cite web | url = http://livefeed.hollywoodreporter.com/2010/05/cw-new-fall-schedule.html | title = CW's new fall schedule: 'Nikita' joins 'Vampire Diaries' | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] - The Live Feed | date = May 20, 2010 | first = James | last = Hibberd | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100523002635/http://livefeed.hollywoodreporter.com/2010/05/cw-new-fall-schedule.html | archivedate = 2010年5月23日 }}</ref>。

尼基塔女郎中的女主角Nikita，由[[Maggie_Q|Maggie Q]]飾演，她的角色是一名已叛離「組織」的間諜及刺客。她現在正致力於推翻組織，一個以前曾招攬她的秘密政府機構。同時，組織在她的叛離後，訓練了一群年輕的新殺手<ref name="synopsis">{{cite web | url = http://www.collider.com/2010/05/20/cw-fall-schedule-supernatural-smallville-one-tree-hill-life-unexpected-90210/ | title = Upfronts: The CW Unveils Their Fall 2010 Schedule; SUPERNATURAL Joins SMALLVILLE on Fridays | work = Collider.com | date = May 20, 2010 | first = Brendan | last = Bettinger | accessdate = 2010-08-05 | archive-date = 2010-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100627074033/http://www.collider.com/2010/05/20/cw-fall-schedule-supernatural-smallville-one-tree-hill-life-unexpected-90210 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 製作 == 
CW電視台一直對製作一套以強悍女性作主角的動作冒險劇集有很大興趣<ref name="lat">{{cite web | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2010/05/upfronts-the-cw-declares-itself-the-cool-place-to-be-.html | title = Upfronts: The CW declares itself 'the cool place to be' | work = [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | date = May 20, 2010 | first = Matea | last = Gold | accessdate = 2010-08-05 | archive-date = 2010-08-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100815062555/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2010/05/upfronts-the-cw-declares-itself-the-cool-place-to-be-.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在2010年1月27日，CW先訂製了尼基塔女郎的首播集<ref name="pilot">{{cite web | url = http://livefeed.hollywoodreporter.com/2010/01/the-cw-orders-la-femme-nikita-pilot.html | title = The CW orders 'La Femme Nikita' remake | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] - The Live Feed | date = January 27, 2010 | first = James | last = Hibberd | accessdate = May 18, 2010 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100501143647/http://livefeed.hollywoodreporter.com/2010/01/the-cw-orders-la-femme-nikita-pilot.html | archivedate = 2010年5月1日 }}</ref>。在2月，[[Maggie_Q|Maggie Q]]被聘作女主角Nikita，而[[夏恩·威斯特|夏恩·威斯特]]則作為角色之一的Michael<ref name="maggieq">{{cite web | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE61I14O20100219 | title = Maggie Q to star as CW's "Nikita" remake | work = [[Reuters|Reuters]] | date = February 19, 2010 | first = Nellie | last = Andreeva | accessdate = May 30, 2010 | archive-date = 2010-10-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101005050242/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE61I14O20100219 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="swest">{{cite web | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE61P1JO20100226 | title = Three "ER" alumni cast in pilots | work = [[Reuters|Reuters]] | date = February 26, 2010 | first = Nellie | last = Andreeva | accessdate = May 30, 2010 | archive-date = 2010-03-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100302165703/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE61P1JO20100226 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。稍後於3月，[[琳德茜·冯塞卡|琳德茜·冯塞卡]]嬴得劇中的其中一個角色，Alex<ref name="lfonsecat">{{cite web | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/television/news/e3i755f10fb8f89b62698b3ffad221a5c6d | title = Several pilots expand casts | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date = March 10, 2010 | first = Nellie | last = Andreeva | accessdate = May 30, 2010 | archive-date = 2010-03-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100314150721/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/television/news/e3i755f10fb8f89b62698b3ffad221a5c6d | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2010年5月18日，尼基塔女郎正式成為秋季檔的新劇<ref name="pickup">{{cite web | url = http://livefeed.hollywoodreporter.com/2010/05/cw-picks-up-nikita-hellcats-life-oth-.html | title = CW picks up 'Nikita,' 'Hellcats,' 'Life,' 'OTH' | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] - The Live Feed | date = May 18, 2010 | first = James | last = Hibberd | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100521043331/http://livefeed.hollywoodreporter.com/2010/05/cw-picks-up-nikita-hellcats-life-oth-.html | archivedate = 2010年5月21日 }}</ref>。2010年版本的電視劇與1990年的電影關係會更加接近，比起1997年版的電視劇更多<ref name="cclat">{{cite web | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2010/07/comiccon-2010-nikita-debut-and-maggie-q-says-dudes-are-gonna-love-it.html | title = COMIC-CON 2010: 'Nikita' debuts and Maggie Q says 'Dudes are gonna love it!' | work = [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | date = July 24, 2010 | first = Jevon | last = Phillips | accessdate = July 25, 2010 | archive-date = 2010-07-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100729122537/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2010/07/comiccon-2010-nikita-debut-and-maggie-q-says-dudes-are-gonna-love-it.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[執行製片人|執行製片人]]Craig Silverstein被擁有版權的華納兄弟電視所接觸，<ref name="igntca"/> Silverstein表示，"我的第一個念頭就是我喜歡尼基塔女郎。我第二個念頭就是，它已經製作過了，它能否變得新鮮？能否做到讓所有人猜不到故事會完結在哪裡？"（"My first thought was I love Nikita. My second thought was, 'it's been done.' Could it be done fresh? Could we have a take where you didn't know where this story would end?"<ref name="igntca">{{cite web | url = http://tv.ign.com/articles/110/1109275p1.html | title = Nikita is Coming to Kick Ass | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = July 29, 2010 | first = Eric | last = Goldman | accessdate = July 30, 2010 | archive-date = 2010-08-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100802143755/http://tv.ign.com/articles/110/1109275p1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>）。因此，此劇比起原著將出現兩大轉變，其中一個是決定故事開始於Nikita叛離以後。Maggie Q表示，"沒有人被告知關於她的故事。沒有人知道她去了哪裡。"（"No one's told her story after the fact. No one knows where she is going."<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.tvguide.com/News/Nikita-Reboot-Work-1020945.aspx | title = Why A Nikita Reboot Can Work | work = [[TV_Guide|TV Guide]] | date = July 25, 2010 | first = Denise | last = Martin | accessdate = July 26, 2010 | archive-date = 2010-07-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100728134014/http://www.tvguide.com/News/Nikita-Reboot-Work-1020945.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>）。另外，新角色Alex亦引入了，並擁有一個意料之外的背景故事<ref name =eonlinetca>{{cite web | url = http://ca.eonline.com/uberblog/watch_with_kristin/b192806_nikita_tvs_hottest_new_star_maggie_q.html | title = Nikita: TV's Hottest New Star, Maggie Q, Is Gonna Knock You Out...No, Really, Beware! | work = [[E!_Online|E! Online]] | date = July 29, 2010 | first = Kristin | last = Dos Santos | accessdate = July 30, 2010 | archive-date = 2013-01-02 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20130102134528/http://ca.eonline.com/uberblog/watch_with_kristin/b192806_nikita_tvs_hottest_new_star_maggie_q.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。劇集將會是每週性的任務或反任務的混合，而首季故事線將探索Nikita與Alex及Michael的關係。<ref name =eonlinetca/>

== 劇情大綱 ==
故事將會集中於一個虛構的部門，隸屬於[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]，又稱為"組織"（Division），"組織"通常都會選擇一些擁有複雜背景的年輕人，經常是獄中或將臨死刑的年輕人，"組織"會偽造他們的死亡，訓練他們成為殺手。新招募者必須懂得關閉感情，變成有效率的殺手。

